org.qbroker.net

Class SNMPConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.net.SNMPConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Connector
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EventTrapSender, SNMPMessenger

    public class SNMPConnector
extends java.lang.Object
implements Connector
    SNMPConnector connects to an SNMP agent or manager and provides the following methods of for SNMP operations: snmpGet(), snmpSet(), sendTrap(), snmpNotify() and receive().

    This is NOT MT-Safe. It requires Java 1.4 or above due to SNMP4J.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
